des:
Exceptional smart lighting made simple with Cree Lighting Connected Max LED Smart Bulbs. Transform your smart home by integrating voice control. Control your home lighting and other devices hands-free.

"Cree Lighting" skill only work with Connected Max Bluetooth + WiFi Smart LED bulbs and do not work with the original Cree Connected Zigbee bulb.

Here’s a step by step guide:
1. Download our "Cree Lighting" app on iOS App Store or Google Play;
2. Launch the app and register a new account (or login if you’re already registered);
3. Turn on Cree Lighting Connected Max LED Smart Bulbs and connect them with “Cree Lighting” app;
4. Download Amazon Alexa app from Amazon Market, Google Play or iOS App Store, and connect your Alexa-enabled device with the Alexa app;
5. Search the Alexa Skills directory for "Cree Lighting";
6. Enable "Cree Lighting" skill, you'll be navigated to the login page, follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
7. Tell Echo "Alexa, discover my devices". Wait for Echo to say "Search complete";
8. Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices.
FYI: You can rename your lights with the Cree Lighting App. So if you rename a bulb “Bedroom Light”, then Alexa will use that same name after discovering the devices.

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on kitchen light"
“Alexa, turn off kitchen light"
“Alexa, dim livingroom light"
“Alexa, brighten livingroom light"
“Alexa, set the livingroom light to 20 percent"
“Alexa, set bedroom light to Blue"
